{"tid":1520754,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"方志恒：831不是終局之戰  《香港人權民主法》是game changer","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T06:08:20.000Z","uid":9028,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1a8956f2329f37a6a13ef94f804dc134b1b7cb","tid":1520754,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"【#即時觀點】831不會是終局之戰。當前香港已處於中美新冷戰的最前線，《香港人權民主法》之通過（以至執行）勢必改寫局勢 &mdash;&mdash; 美國參議院民主黨領袖舒默，在昨天的大搜捕後，已力促國會在9月9日復會後，應立即通過法案。我明白大家對香港局勢憂心忡忡，但我們必須保持冷靜和耐心，從地緣政治的視野（而不止是中港關係的格局）思考下一步。<br />\n<br />\n831 will NOT be the endgame. Hong Kong is already in the forefront of US-China New Cold War, the passage of the Hong Kong Human Rights &amp; Democracy Act (and its implementation) will be the game changer &mdash;&mdash; After the mass arrest yesterday, the US Senate Minority Leader Senator Chuck Schumer has already urged to quickly pass the Act when the Congress resumes its session on 9 September. I understand that everyone is very worried about the current situation in Hong Kong, but we must stay clam and think about the next step in the context of geopolitics (instead of merely adopting a China-Hong Kong framework).<br />\n<br />\n▋延伸閱讀Further reading<br />\n香港在中美新冷戰：自由世界前哨？紅色中國前哨？／方志恒<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K5XGHn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2K5XGHn&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=0d216644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2K5XGHn</a><br />\nHong Kong and the US-China New Cold War／Brian C. H. Fong<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HMt7El\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HMt7El&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=07101b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HMt7El</a><br />\n<br />\nl://<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/2404330493021727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbrianfonghk%2Fposts%2F2404330493021727&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=a845a640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/2404330493021727</a><br />\n方志恒"},{"pid":"c4b5c30592b2c3fe4cd6ca65c932d427d8b206f5","tid":1520754,"uid":9028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/2404330493021727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbrianfonghk%2Fposts%2F2404330493021727&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2VDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=f15a2400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/brianfonghk/posts/2404330493021727</a>"},{"pid":"f86b4a9e4eeb7e3952f7a0d8e879630cb4b03038","tid":1520754,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdMVZe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdMVZe3.gif&h=dfb69189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f42d4fdef1bb10eb050cb3c9e85db86a84a816ce","tid":1520754,"uid":35842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtWu3Kv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtWu3Kv.jpg&h=c828d33c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20e5f470912d2f231ddd08a9e77699bd16e27488","tid":1520754,"uid":90960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f86b4a9e4eeb7e3952f7a0d8e879630cb4b03038","tid":1520754,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BdMVZe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdMVZe3.gif&h=dfb69189&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"有聲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5c2370ae279e39637e6c7ac11f08614ae52840","tid":1520754,"uid":287829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci